Title: Iceman
Plot: When a supposedly frozen to death Marine turns out alive on Ducky's autopsy table, the NCIS team has to find out about the victim's movements last few days to uncover what happened to him and who left him for dead. As the investigation progresses, the team learns about the victim's trip to Baghdad via a private cargo plane and discovers a link to Gibbs' past.
GuestStars: Muse Watson, Scottie Thompson, Navid Negahban, Stephanie Venditto, Steven Elder
